title: Boho Chic Airstream with private yard
posting_body: ['Boho Chic Modernized Streamline Airstream-type accommodations tucked into gorgeous Topanga Canyon.', 'Just around the corner from the State Park’s endless trails and sights.', 'And a short drive to Topanga Surf Break, the beach and the Pacific Ocean.', 'Open your door to a private yard with comfortable lounge chairs.', 'Freshly renovated accommodations.', 'Modern amenities include a kitchenette, comfortable bathroom with shower, private yard, cushy double bed and a single bed (couch).', 'A 5-minute walk (30-second drive) to Topanga Village which includes restaurants, shopping, and entertainment.', 'This property is in a funky little RV park called nestled amongst mature trees and greenery.', 'There are only 5 units in the community; 4 classic aluminium trailers including Spartan, Streamline, and Silver Streak and a Tiny Home.', 'Each of the units are well spaced from one another.', 'A good isolated escape from the congestion of the city, with easy access to enjoy nature and the outdoors.', 'No pets, please.', 'Available August 1, 2022.', 'Monthly ($1,995) rental/', 'Weekly ($665).', 'Email for availability.']
